@startuml
actor User
boundary ModeratePostsView
control ModerationController
entity POST

ref over User, ModeratePostsView, ModerationController, POST : Search Pending Posts

User -> ModeratePostsView : Select post to moderate
activate ModeratePostsView
ModeratePostsView -> ModerationController : getPost(id)
activate ModerationController
ModerationController -> POST : Query existing post
activate POST

alt Post exists
    POST --> ModerationController : Post data
    ModerationController --> ModeratePostsView : Post data
    ModeratePostsView --> User : Display existing data
    User -> ModeratePostsView : Select moderation decision
    User -> ModeratePostsView : Click button "Moderate"

    ModeratePostsView -> ModeratePostsView : Validate input information
    alt Valid input
        ModeratePostsView -> ModerationController : moderatePost(id, decision)
        ModerationController -> POST : Validate post data

        alt Valid data
            POST --> ModerationController : Validation success
            ModerationController -> POST : Update post status
            POST --> ModerationController : Post updated
            ModerationController --> ModeratePostsView : Success response
            ModeratePostsView --> User : Notify moderation success
            User -> ModeratePostsView : Confirm success notification
        else Invalid data
            POST --> ModerationController : Validation error
            ModerationController --> ModeratePostsView : Error response
            ModeratePostsView --> User : Notify invalid data
            User -> ModeratePostsView : Confirm error notification
        end
    else Invalid input
        ModeratePostsView --> User : Notify invalid input
        User -> ModeratePostsView : Confirm error notification
    end
else Post not found
    POST --> ModerationController : Null
    ModerationController --> ModeratePostsView : Error response
    ModeratePostsView --> User : Notify post not found
    User -> ModeratePostsView : Confirm error notification
end
deactivate POST
deactivate ModerationController
deactivate ModeratePostsView
@enduml